OL,4,CBristol mum facing #85k bill to extend
OL,5,Clife with her son
OL,6, A mum is facing an #85,000 bill to
OL,7, undergo treatment she hopes will allow
OL,8, her to see her son take his GCSEs.
OL,10,FSarah, 49, was diagnosed with
OL,11,Fglioblastoma, an aggressive form of
OL,12,Fcancer, in her brain in November 2020.
OL,14,FAfter she was given 14-16 months to
OL,15,Flive, Sarah's friends raised more than
OL,16,F#37,000 in a week to enable her to
OL,17,Fstart dendritic cell therapy in
OL,18,FGermany.
OL,20,FShe said: "My son needs a mum and there
OL,21,Fisn't an amount you can put on that."
